Class Jwt

java.lang.Object
iu.auth.config.Jwt
All Implemented Interfaces:
IuWebToken
public class Jwt extends Object implements IuWebToken
Basic JWT claims IuWebToken implementation.

May be extended to implement token-specific claim values.
